. Covers Broad Spectrum
By CHARLES SMITH and ANDY ISAACS
How do Grinnell’s faculty go about fulfilling the college's hopes
that they will device themselves to similarly achievement? We
asked the members oi the science departments for this first art-
isle, and the answers were quite
impressive. Virtually every professor is engaged in some re
search or writing projects
For example, in the physics
department, Roger Hansen is
currently on leave, experimenting with nuclear specloscopy at
the University of marcus in
Denmark. Beryl Clotfelter, the
department head, is studying
connectivity in walls or glass
tubes during electrical dis
charge. He intense to publish
his ﬁthings soon. Bruce Thomas
plans to publish, in conjunction
with the Argonne National Laboratory, a paper on the optical
properties of polystyrenes.
Wayne penny, having returned
ircm a year in india, is working on solid state electronics
